message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you this great product. I think you'll really love it. I'm willing to sell it to you for $120.
Hi Alice, thanks for the offer. I'm interested, but $120 is a bit higher than I was hoping for. I'm willing to pay $100 for it. Let me know what you think.
Hi Bob, I understand you're looking for a better deal, but I have to make a profit. I'm willing to meet you in the middle at $110. What do you think?
